Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.24,0:07:04.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得让自己的身体准备好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Gotta trick your body into going to sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在全世界醒来时入睡\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}when the rest of the world is waking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都是同样的食物  同样的地点\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Same meal, same place every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则我就别想合眼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}or I don't sleep a wink.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.34,0:07:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过谢谢你这顿饭\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But I do appreciate the meal
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和热可可\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and the hot cocoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.31,0:07:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般人家会问很多问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Normally people ask more questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-比如呢  -"你是谁"啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}- Such as? - "Who are you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"你想我怎么样"啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}"What do you want with me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"这到底是怎么回事"啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}"What the hell's going on?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.98,0:07:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[西班牙语]\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Que sera, sera.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.06,0:07:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该来的  自然会来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Whatever will be, will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Took me a long time to see it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.59,0:07:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凡事都是命中注定  天意安排\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}but there's an order to things, a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:44.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所发生的一切都是注定的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And everything that happens is part of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}including you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.31,0:07:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过要是你乐意\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But if it makes you feel any better,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.29,0:07:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"这到底是怎么回事"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的老大让我跟你谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}My boss wanted me to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.58,0:07:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是说你我应该\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Which means you and I are supposed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.77,0:07:57.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起合作某件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}to do something together,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:07:59.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很重要的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:02.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这工作听着都古怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Sounds like you got a weird job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你老大让我干啥\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What's your boss want us to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.01,0:08:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不说\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}She won't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她比较希望我自己弄清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}She likes it better when I figure it out myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这老大听着都古怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Sounds like you have a weird boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我得去公园走走了  风雨无阻\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Well, now I go to the park for a walk, rain or shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,0:08:25.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新鲜空气能帮我入眠\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Fresh air helps me have good dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你乐意的话  欢迎陪我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're more than welcome to join if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么偷偷接近我可不明智啊  哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You should know better than to try to sneak up on me, Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.48,0:08:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是来欢迎我重回纽约吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Did you come to welcome me back to New York?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实  我们是为威尔斯先生而来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Actually, we're here for Mr. Wells.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.00,0:09:01.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的号码早上7:04跳了出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}His number came 7:04 this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那无所不能的机器\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Your multifaceted machine
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是神秘莫测啊  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}sure does work in mysterious ways, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:09.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次倒不太难测\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}In this case perhaps not that mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里瑟先生和肖女士进入他工作的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}When Mr. Reese and Ms. Shaw accessed the security system
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.93,0:09:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那栋大楼的安保系统后\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}in the building where he works,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现你接近了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}they found you approaching him
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.58,0:09:21.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好在早上7:04\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}at precisely 7:04 a.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.82,0:09:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我初步查看了他的网络数据资料\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I've prepared a preliminary study of his digital footprint,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据我判断\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and in my estimation
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赛勒斯・威尔斯生活中最危险的就是你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}the most dangerous thing in Cyrus Wells's life is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.51,0:09:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你的计划如何  格罗夫斯女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Whatever your plan is, Ms. Groves,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.18,0:09:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你会害他送命\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I believe you're gonna get him killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.40,0:09:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs20\bord0\shad0\b1\pos(195,180)\fad(0,300)\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fsp10\c&H00FFFFFF\K30}疑犯追踪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.40,0:09:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs12\bord0\shad0\b1\pos(190,196)\fad(0,300)\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\c&H00FFFFFF\K30}第三季第十七集
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.03,0:09:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别紧张  哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Relax, Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.08,0:09:49.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会有人送命的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Nobody's getting anybody killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.55,0:09:52.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赛勒斯跟我在一起非常安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Cyrus is perfectly safe with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:55.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然机器把他的号码发给我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}If the machine sent us his number,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:09:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可能意味着是你把威尔斯先生置于危险之中了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}it may mean that you are placing Mr. Wells at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者意味着我来保护他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Or it could mean I'm here to protect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坦白说  哈罗德  要跟上\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Honestly, Harold, keeping up with everything
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.84,0:10:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机器对我说的每一句话可不容易\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}the machine whispers in my ear can be tricky,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.55,0:10:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是现在我还废了一只耳朵\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}especially now that I'm down to one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.03,0:10:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没听说过我跟主控者的聊天吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Did you not hear about my chat with Control?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她很有趣\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}She's fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟个没必要的镫骨切除术一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}in an unnecessary stapedectomy kind of way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.91,0:10:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还挺怀念立体声音乐\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}but I do miss music in stereo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.57,0:10:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很遗憾\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机器给了我一份工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The machine offered me a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:28.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她可没说这会很容易\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}She never said it would be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底是什么工作呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And what job is that exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.83,0:10:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是拯救世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Trying to save the world, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.45,0:10:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阻止第二台机器的出现\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}By preventing the emergence of a second machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"撒马利亚人"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Samaritan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:45.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基因编程  目标明确  几近完成\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Genetically programmed, fully targetable, and nearly complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.21,0:10:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"撒马利亚人"严重威胁到了我们的机器  哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Samaritan presents a serious threat to our machine, Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而德西玛想要把它激活\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and Decima's trying to bring it to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.78,0:10:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你想看到两位上帝开战\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Do you really want to see what it looks like
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.27,0:10:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是何等场面吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}when two Gods go to war?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.60,0:11:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许你更应该担心的是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Maybe you should be more worried
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.45,0:11:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"撒马利亚人"上线之后会造成什么后果\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}about what happens when Samaritan comes online
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不是担心一位清洁工\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}than about what happens to some janitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对那位清洁工了解多少  格罗夫斯女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}How much do you know about this janitor, Ms. Groves?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他对于形而上学决定论的看法挺有意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}He's got some interesting ideas about metaphysical determinism,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得他是[德国女导演]多丽丝・戴的粉丝\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and I think he's a Doris Day fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道他有福德姆学院金融学硕士学位吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Do you know that he has an MBA in finance from Fordham?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.86,0:11:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道他在35岁时已经是千万富翁了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Do you know he was a multimillionaire by the age of 35?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.34,0:11:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道他2009年之后就不在华尔街上班了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Do you know he hasn't worked on Wall Street since 2009?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本不关心为什么吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Would you even care to know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许你应该让机器\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Perhaps you should ask the machine
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:37.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多告诉你一点塞勒斯・威尔斯的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}for a bit more information about Cyrus Wells
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.91,0:11:40.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再对他妄下结论  随意轻视\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}before you deem him insignificant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.79,0:11:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没事的  我保证\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}He'll be fine, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:46.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道听起来都古怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I know it seems weird,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我现在是好人了噢  哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}but I'm one of the good guys now, Harold.
