Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:12:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从下数第三  从右数第十五  在你身后\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Third from the bottom, 15th on the right, behind you.
