Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.73,0:15:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有把枪就好了  可是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So a gun would be nice, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:15:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是面面俱到\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}you think of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,催泪瓦斯  憋住气\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Tear gas. Hold your breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.63,0:16:09.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  狙击手怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Wait. What about the sniper?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Trust me.
