Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:46.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的名字出现在了他们截获的一封密件上\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}because his name came up in a secret communique they intercepted
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.82,0:16:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来自德西玛公司\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}from Decima.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.83,0:16:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来根不是我们最大的麻烦了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I don't think Root's our biggest problem anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.53,0:17:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙是什么人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Who are those guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.54,0:17:05.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉过你事情会越来越有趣\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I told you things were gonna get interesting.
