Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.87,0:17:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不该跑吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Shouldn't we run?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:20.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听不清老大的话了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I can't hear my boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你二十块\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Here's $20.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么停下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Why are we stopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.75,0:17:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有更多人从那四个人的方向来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Because there are more where those four came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这样能让你脱身\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And this is the quickest way to get you out of here
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:36.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不用开枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}without shooting someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们铐你时\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Keep your shoulders relaxed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肩膀要放松\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}when they put the handcuffs on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.99,0:17:44.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举起手来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Hands in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举起手来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Hands in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.73,0:17:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞勒斯安全了  芬奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Cyrus is safe, Finch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:02.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们得让弗斯科保护好他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But we'll need Fusco's help to keep it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格罗夫斯女士呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And Ms. Groves?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.11,0:18:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不见了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.54,0:18:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西玛派来的人也不见了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So are the boys from Decima.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.07,0:18:09.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道塞勒斯到底干了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Do we have any idea what Cyrus did
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才会惹到德西玛和"时刻警惕"了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}to piss off both them and Vigilance?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就目前情况来看  一无所知\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}As far as I can tell, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过现在  我开始怀疑比起旧工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But whatever's going on, I'm starting to suspect
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的新工作与此事牵连更多\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}that it has more to do with his new job than his old one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我黑进了塞勒斯做清洁服务的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I hacked the computer system
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家公司的电脑系统\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}at the janitorial service that employs Cyrus
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.51,0:18:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现他们最近对他做了背景调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and discovered they recently ran a background check on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.85,0:18:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么样的清洁工需要背景调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What kind of janitor needs a background check?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,值得一查\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Something to look into
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待我们联系上肖女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}when we reconnect with Ms. Shaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:36.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枪战开始时我便失去了她的信号\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I lost her signal when the shooting started.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.39,0:18:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说她看到了狙击手\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}She said she saw a sniper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.96,0:18:41.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我在这儿没看到她\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But I don't see any sign of her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.27,0:18:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肖和塞勒斯一比\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Between Shaw and Cyrus,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁更需要帮助不言而喻\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I think I know who needs our help more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.15,0:18:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们只得相信肖女士的自救能力了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Then I'm afraid we'll have to trust Ms. Shaw to take care of herself.
