Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你一时半会死不了  那我们来聊聊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Now that you're not gonna die, we can have a little chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:18:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要去医院\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So you need a hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.44,0:19:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要知道为何大家都追杀那位清洁工\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and I need to know why everyone's after the janitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你欠我个狙击手\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You owe me a sniper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科利尔  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}This is Collier, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少是你的化名\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Or at least that's your alias?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.74,0:19:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Can't say I know yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.88,0:19:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就叫你机会目标好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So I'll just call you a target of opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.54,0:19:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"时刻警惕"到这来是为了审问塞勒斯・威尔斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Vigilance came here to interrogate Cyrus Wells,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在却为你而来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}but now we're here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从你打斗的招式可以看出\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}See, based on the way you fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.07,0:19:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你曾是一名为美利坚效忠的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I think you were a clandestine operative
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.78,0:19:29.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密行动成员\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}for the good old U.S. Of A.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.04,0:19:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但从你保护的人来看\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But based on the people you protect,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.05,0:19:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在应该不是了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I think you're not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.28,0:19:37.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我估计是因为他们背叛了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And I'm guessing it's because they betrayed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是准备开枪打死我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Are you guys gonna shoot again
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.52,0:19:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说话说死我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}or just talk me to death?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上我更想知道你要说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Actually I'm more interested in what you have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.05,0:19:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我自行封住了出口\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So I've taken the liberty of sealing off the exits.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.51,0:19:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为交换  我需要你告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Now in exchange for everything you know
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.26,0:19:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所知道关于"撒马利亚人"的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}about the Samaritan system
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.51,0:19:55.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有他的建造者们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and the people that are trying to build it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.24,0:19:56.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我准备给你提供\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm prepared to offer you something
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:19:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝无仅有的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}that no one else can--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.95,0:20:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向出卖了你的政府复仇\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Revenge on the government that betrayed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.71,0:20:05.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我拒绝呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And if I refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.04,0:20:06.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用本杰明・富兰克林的话说\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}In the words of Benjamin Franklin,
