Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.80,0:28:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界上最快的电脑\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The fastest computer ever built.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.74,0:28:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦斯威尔是国安局实验室的幌子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Maxwell's the corporate cover for an NSA lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.80,0:29:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两天前\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And two days ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.11,0:29:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实验室内部人员发送了这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}somebody working in that lab sent this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.14,0:29:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正硬笔行书简体\fs22\shad0\bord0\c&H151B25&\frz339\move(166.574,114.558,176.584,170.23,0,430)}你应该会想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.77,0:29:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.18,0:29:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芬奇  怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Okay, Finch, what am I missing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.91,0:29:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是电脑科学家给同行写的纸条\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's a note from one computer scientist to another,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.91,0:29:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面写着超导处理器的规格\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}detailing the specifications of a superconducting processor,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.09,0:29:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比现行处理器要快上三倍\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}three times faster than anything now available.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.88,0:29:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由于政府不肯将其卖给德西玛\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And since the government's not about to sell it to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.63,0:29:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们打算利用塞勒斯去偷\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Decima plans to use Cyrus to steal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.03,0:29:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初撒马利亚人系统崩溃  是因为当时\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The original Samaritan crashed because a chip
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.47,0:29:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,运算速度足够快的芯片还没有制造出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}fast enough to run it hadn't been built yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.67,0:29:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两天前  有人制造出来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Two days ago, somebody built it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.75,0:29:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西玛有了软件\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Decima has the software.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.84,0:29:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在  他们想要硬件\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Now they want the hardware.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.99,0:29:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在  我更担心的是塞勒斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Right now, I'm more worried about Cyrus.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.14,0:29:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一旦开了门\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}As soon as he opens that door,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.35,0:29:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西玛就会杀了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Decima's gonna kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.28,0:29:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你要去找里瑟先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I suppose you'll be joining Mr. Reese.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.80,0:29:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Not just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.17,0:29:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西玛之前断开了我和机器的连接\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Decima's severed my link to the machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.96,0:29:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一小会儿  但她不喜欢那样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Temporarily, but she didn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.31,0:29:59.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.29,0:30:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她要你把这些接进这个里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}she wants you to patch these into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.12,0:30:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次你对我们该帮不帮\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The last time you didn't help us when you should have,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.41,0:30:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人送了命\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}people died.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.97,0:30:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装置装好后\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And once this device is installed,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.84,0:30:32.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会救哪个\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}which will you save:
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.69,0:30:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芯片  还是塞勒斯・威尔斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The chip or Cyrus Wells?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.82,0:30:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你害他身陷危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Since it was you who put him in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.07,0:30:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Fine, Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.49,0:30:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's all my fault--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.18,0:30:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我跟机器的错  满意了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Mine and the machine's. Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.26,0:30:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也不  但我的确相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Far from it, but I do believe
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.89,0:30:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该从中吸取教训  戒狂戒傲\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}that there's a lesson here about hubris.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.81,0:30:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最了解"狂傲"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}If anyone would know about hubris,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.33,0:31:02.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫过于造出上帝的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}it would be the man who built God.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.56,0:31:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她很担心你  哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}She's worried about you, Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.79,0:31:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都很担心你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We both are.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.72,0:31:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去三个月里  你平均每晚\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The past three months, you've slept an average
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.36,0:31:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只睡了四个小时\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}of four hours per night.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.74,0:31:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的事与你无关  格罗夫斯女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}My problems are no concern of yours, Ms. Groves.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.21,0:31:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果拿出这十分之一的劲头\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Perhaps if you had 1/10 as much interest
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.49,0:31:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关心塞勒斯  他现在可能就不会\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}in Cyrus's welfare, he might not be about--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.82,0:31:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按你自己的定义\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}By your own definition,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.83,0:31:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞勒斯是无关号码\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Cyrus is irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.99,0:31:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人都会与某些人相关\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Everyone is relevant to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.99,0:31:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}S01E22开头
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.53,0:31:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人在他生命中的每一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}That man has spent every day of his life
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.33,0:31:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都相信有所谓的天意安排\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}believing that there is actually some sort of higher plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.14,0:31:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是人类的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}That's the problem with humans--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.68,0:31:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们总是待在原地  期望着\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}They just sit around, hoping that
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.27,0:31:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人来解决一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}someone will fix things.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.52,0:31:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是没人会  没人在乎\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But no one will. No one cares.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.23,0:31:53.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙无穷无尽\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The universe is infinite
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.96,0:31:56.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混乱  冷酷\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and chaotic and cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.75,0:31:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从来就没有天意安排\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And there has never been a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.30,0:32:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到现在\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}At least not till now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.41,0:32:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想知道他们死那天的安排吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You wanna know what the plan was the day they died?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.46,0:32:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天的安排是有人想赚1500万\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The plan was for someone to make $15 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.18,0:32:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一家大银行的高管要他们死\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}An executive at a big bank wanted them dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.68,0:32:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他花钱雇了一个有能力\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}so he wired the money to someone with the skills,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.27,0:32:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有资源  又毫无道德感的人去安排\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}resources, and moral depravity to make that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.27,0:32:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人就是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And that someone was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.94,0:32:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好笑的是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And the punch line
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.55,0:32:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的机器一直要我去救塞勒斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}is that your machine keeps telling me to save Cyrus.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.93,0:32:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底把它毁得有多惨\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}How badly did you have to break it
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.83,0:32:59.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能让它如此在乎生命\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}to make it care about people so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.61,0:33:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这并没有毁它  它以此存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}That didn't break it. It's what made it work.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.85,0:33:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我教会了机器生命的重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It was only after I taught the machine that people mattered,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.71,0:33:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它才能够帮助人类\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}that it could begin to be able to help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.91,0:33:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想如此对你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'd like to do the same thing for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.54,0:33:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请允许我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}if you'd let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.76,0:33:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"撒马利亚人"上线三十分钟内\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}In the first 30 minutes after Samaritan comes online,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.72,0:33:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多人会送命\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}a lot of people are gonna be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.57,0:33:47.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首当其中的四个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But they're gonna start with four:
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.29,0:33:54.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你  我  你的宠物  和肖\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You, me, your helper monkey, and Shaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.06,0:33:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,届时任何人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And there won't be a damn thing anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.64,0:34:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括你的机器  都无能为力\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}including your machine, can do to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.52,0:34:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得我不在乎生命  哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You think I don't care about people, Harold?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.92,0:34:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了这么多  都是为了救你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm doing all of this to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.42,0:34:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  医生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Sorry, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.86,0:34:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没时间预约\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I didn't have time to make an appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.08,0:34:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我知道你会为我破例\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But I know you'll make an exception for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.41,0:34:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.99,0:34:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎么知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And how do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.53,0:34:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如我知道我可以一枪打穿你的手\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The same way I know I can put a bullet through your hand
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.93,0:34:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你来不及拨打911报警\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}before you can dial 911.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.88,0:34:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如我知道你是四百公里内最好的耳鼻喉科医生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The same way I know you're the best otolaryngologist in 250 miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.91,0:34:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  你想要什么  药吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Okay, uh, what do you want? Drugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.89,0:34:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.44,0:34:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过来点[麻醉剂]利多卡因倒是不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Although a little lidocaine would be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.52,0:34:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次的手术我没用到\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I didn't get any the last time.
